Strength:

3-3-3-3
*pause for 3 sec at the bottom of each rep
build up load each set.

Metcon:
For time:

400m Run
30 Power Snatches (#60/40)
30 Cal Row
30 Thrusters (#60/40)

5 Burpee Box Jumps
